text: Carlos Milthaler (born 12 June 1971) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
